_sText:
So I was pretty fed up with the version of officeworld released by plywood on here, so I figured it's time for an update.

Based on the highly popular cs_ map office, it has buyzones and supports upto 32 players (tested, works fine).

this is a map intended for use on GunGame
servers, but can also be played on regular servers. It has 
a cs_office theme and contains useful hiding spots, yet is also laid
out to deter campers
